folder: Van Duzer Street & Sands Street, Staten Island, NY
original_title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Sands Street
text:
Van Duzer Street, west side, south from Sands to Prospect Streets. In the right background appears the steeple of the Evangelical Lutheran Church, on St. Pauls
Avenue.
May 25, 1935
P. L. Sperr
